Include in the static context of each query module a namespace binding of the
                prefix "bin" to the namespace URI http://expath.org/ns/binary
                (subject to the same rules as other predeclared namespace bindings: see 
                );

Include in the static context of each query module a namespace binding of the
                prefix "file" to the namespace URI http://expath.org/ns/file
                (subject to the same rules as other predeclared namespace bindings: see 
                );
